{"tid":2024462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和支那接軌","createTime":"2020-05-19T15:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T12:08:08.000Z","uid":78243,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8ef28f385c148a11ea6c0a45db394cecb8f14a","tid":2024462,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和支那接軌，<br />\n主權移交後要拼盡全力 奶共，拿取權力。<br />\n會首先開放自由行. 新移民, 先換一代血。<br />\n然後一邊洗腦一邊拿利誘，以最快速度上位。<br />\n成功換第一代血後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。<br />\n(送中，國歌法，廿三條，去逼害反對的人)<br />\n24年 假一國兩制, 將來就可以用法律封殺香港各個反動份子。<br />\n又要負責幫港共和 支那，中共聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為國家制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以統一台灣。<br />\n簡直是世界主力核心。<br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"1887dfefaa9c47a40efcf3c93488a8460f89ba66","tid":2024462,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"「突發」文匯報=fake news<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8672493070787a7b97b56230b924b3e1b9c7e0f","tid":2024462,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"其實我地可唔可以係海外建立一個香港人專屬既Kickstarter<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9427c873678aa084c7c9517de83ad15bc8c3c16d","tid":2024462,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caedcaf69eb150ca3e8f95d81f870cde892983c0","tid":2024462,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af315ddb46c8b1484484bc00ec311a6c4bd8a4c5","tid":2024462,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"